                  MethodType.methodType(Class.class, String.class));
  
          Class<?> resolvedClass = (Class<?>) classLookup.invoke(
                  INPUT_STREAM_REQUEST_ENTITY_CLASS_NAME);
  
          assertThat(resolvedClass).isSameAs(InputStreamRequestEntity.class);
      }
  
